# AI FORGE PROTOCOL (A.F.P)
> Evaluating the Structural Integrity of Cognitive Systems through Systematic Perturbation.

---

### 🛡️ The Mission: Beyond Static Benchmarks
Most AI evaluation (MMLU, GSM8K) is **state-blind**. It measures *what* a model knows, but not *how* it reasons under internal stress. **The Forge** is a diagnostic harness designed to measure the "load-bearing" capacity of an AI's internal logic. 

We don't just ask the AI questions; we perturb its internal state variables (e.g., simulated energy levels, emotional context, or memory salience) to see if its reasoning chain remains coherent or collapses into hallucination.

---

